      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(5) Muhammad bin Ya’qoob narrated from some of his companions from Ahmad bin Mihran from Muhammad bin Ali that al-Husayn bin Abul Ala’ had asked Abu Abdullah as-Sadiq (as): “Is the world left without an imam?” He replied: “No, it is not.”"
